Subject: Re: [VB] Metal Practice

It depends on the metal!  I'll either use an IR cutoff wheel or
a HF body saw.  The body saw cuts very cleanly, and you make your
own blades by taking a high quality metal hacksaw blade and cutting
it into 3 pieces.

